2
00:00:02,628 --> 00:00:04,087
I NEED THE PROMISE
OF A BRAND NEW PROJECT.

3
00:00:04,171 --> 00:00:05,047
CLARE:
I CAN'T WAIT TO SEE
WHAT YOU DECIDE-

4
00:00:05,130 --> 00:00:06,465
ELI:
WHOA! SOMEONE'S IN A HURRY.

5
00:00:06,548 --> 00:00:08,050
BECKY:
SORRY, ELI! CLARE!

6
00:00:10,302 --> 00:00:11,803
HI.

7
00:00:12,429 --> 00:00:13,805
HEY, GIRL.

8
00:00:13,889 --> 00:00:15,390
OH!

9
00:00:16,266 --> 00:00:17,809
WOW.
BEAUTIFUL RING.

10
00:00:17,893 --> 00:00:18,435
TELL ANYONE
AND YOU'RE DEAD.

11
00:00:18,519 --> 00:00:20,020
OKEY-DOKEY.

12
00:00:23,315 --> 00:00:25,150
JENNA, I FEEL LIKE
I HAVEN'T SEEN YOU IN FOREVER!

13
00:00:25,234 --> 00:00:27,027
GUESS WHAT?!

14
00:00:27,110 --> 00:00:29,530
NEVER MIND,
I CAN'T KEEP A SECRET.

15
00:00:29,613 --> 00:00:32,241
SEVEN PLANE TICKETS
TO VEGAS.

16
00:00:32,324 --> 00:00:33,784
AS IF YOUR PARENTS WOULD
LET YOU GO TO "SIN CITY."

17
00:00:33,867 --> 00:00:35,911
NO, SILLY.

18
00:00:35,994 --> 00:00:36,954
THEY'RE FOR THE STUDENT
COUNCIL FUNDRAISER.

19
00:00:37,037 --> 00:00:38,789
I GOT AN AIRLINE
TO DONATE THEM.

20
00:00:38,872 --> 00:00:40,457
THEY WERE ONLY GOING
TO GIVE ME SIX,

21
00:00:40,541 --> 00:00:42,084
BUT I SAID,
"HOW ABOUT LUCKY SEVEN?"

22
00:00:42,167 --> 00:00:42,960
WE'RE GONNA RAISE
SO MUCH MONEY

23
00:00:43,043 --> 00:00:44,253
FOR THE SCHOOL!
(GIGGLES)

24
00:00:44,336 --> 00:00:46,797
ADAM:
OH. WATCH IT, DANCEY PANTS.

25
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:48,048
BECKY:
SORRY, ADAM.
ARE YOU OKAY?

26
00:00:48,131 --> 00:00:50,843
I'M FINE;
YOU WEIGH LIKE A POUND.

27
00:00:50,926 --> 00:00:52,970
BECKY:
HAPPY ROMEO AND JULES
IS DONE?

28
00:00:53,053 --> 00:00:54,221
UM, NOT THAT YOU SHOULD
BE HAPPY.

29
00:00:54,304 --> 00:00:56,014
ALTHOUGH YOU COULD BE,

30
00:00:56,098 --> 00:00:56,974
'CUZ YOU'RE ENTITLED
TO WHATEVER FEELINGS YOU WANT.

31
00:00:57,057 --> 00:00:58,642
(SCHOOL BELL RINGS)

32
00:00:58,725 --> 00:01:00,227
I HAVE CLASS.

33
00:01:00,310 --> 00:01:01,645
BECKY:
GREAT.

34
00:01:01,728 --> 00:01:03,230
HAVE FUN!

35
00:01:03,981 --> 00:01:05,983
"HAVE FUN?"

36
00:01:06,066 --> 00:01:08,235
UGH! DID I SOUND
LIKE A MORON?

37
00:01:08,318 --> 00:01:10,362
YES! YES, YOU DID!

38
00:01:10,445 --> 00:01:12,489
BECAUSE YOU LIKE ADAM!

39
00:01:12,573 --> 00:01:13,323
I HAVEN'T BEEN ABLE
TO STOP THINKING ABOUT HIM

40
00:01:13,407 --> 00:01:14,241
SINCE I SANG IN THE MUSICAL.

41
00:01:14,324 --> 00:01:15,826
WHAT AM I GONNA DO?

42
00:01:15,909 --> 00:01:17,160
BECAUSE OF
THE TRANSGENDER THING?

43
00:01:17,244 --> 00:01:18,954
ADAM'S A BOY.

44
00:01:19,037 --> 00:01:20,080
I WOULDN'T HAVE FEELINGS
FOR HIM IF HE WEREN'T.

45
00:01:20,163 --> 00:01:21,498
THEN WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?

46
00:01:21,582 --> 00:01:23,792
HE ALREADY ASKED ME OUT
AND I BLEW IT.

47
00:01:23,876 --> 00:01:25,586
HOW DO I GET HIM
TO ASK AGAIN?

48
00:01:25,669 --> 00:01:27,171
YOU COULD DO
THE ASKING.

49
00:01:28,630 --> 00:01:30,132
I COULD.

50
00:01:32,259 --> 00:01:34,386
IT'S TIME
FOR A FRESH START.

51
